  "detailed_description": "You are reborn from the void.<br>As your Ego, explore the Maze and take Shape.<br><br>Shape is an experimental game about perception and an invitation to introspection.<br><br>The player must escape from a maze, with sole ally his shadow.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375270/extras/6d086a73d17c2964b89e5f4b4aa64cbb.poster.avif?t=1600599548\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375270/extras/6d086a73d17c2964b89e5f4b4aa64cbb.webm?t=1600599548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375270/extras/6d086a73d17c2964b89e5f4b4aa64cbb.mp4?t=1600599548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><br>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Freedom to Explore At Your Pace<br></li><li>Maze Filled With Puzzles and Tricks<br></li><li>Conversations With Your Shadow<br></li><li>Your Own Shape</li></ul><br><strong>Puzzles</strong><br>Explore and interact with the maze.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375270/extras/816a8db2b274af3c715171a94806aef8.poster.avif?t=1600599548\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375270/extras/816a8db2b274af3c715171a94806aef8.webm?t=1600599548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375270/extras/816a8db2b274af3c715171a94806aef8.mp4?t=1600599548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Shadow</strong><br>You are the shadow you cast.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375270/extras/d057062e855cd4b250f0a78685ce49b4.poster.avif?t=1600599548\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375270/extras/d057062e855cd4b250f0a78685ce49b4.webm?t=1600599548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375270/extras/d057062e855cd4b250f0a78685ce49b4.mp4?t=1600599548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
